ly affected by seeing effects. Taken at\nface value, our results suggest that environment plays a minor role in\ndetermining the thin and thick disc sizes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 29 Apr 2008 16:46:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
